<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Interspousal Transfer Deed - {{ county }} County, California</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            font-size: 12pt;
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .document-container {
            max-width: 8.5in;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0.75in;
        }
        .header-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .document-title {
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .recording-info {
            border: 2px solid #000;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }
        .recording-grid {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .recording-row {
            display: table-row;
        }
        .recording-cell {
            display: table-cell;
            padding: 5px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
        .recording-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 30%;
        }
        .interspousal-notice {
            border: 2px solid #4169e1;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .interspousal-notice-title {
            font-size: 14pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4169e1;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .interspousal-notice-text {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4169e1;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .parties-section {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .parties-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .legal-description {
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            border-left: 4px solid #333;
        }
        .legal-description-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .transfer-clause {
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: justify;
            font-weight: bold;
            background-color: #fff8dc;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .property-characterization {
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f0fff0;
            border: 2px solid #32cd32;
        }
        .characterization-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #228b22;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .tax-exemption {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            border: 1px solid #999;
        }
        .execution-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        .signature-block {
            margin: 40px 0;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            width: 300px;
            height: 40px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 20px 10px 0;
        }
        .signature-label {
            font-size: 10pt;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .notary-section {
            margin-top: 60px;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            padding: 20px;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        .notary-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .notary-text {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .notary-signature-block {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .legal-considerations {
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #fffacd;
            border: 1px solid #daa520;
            border-left: 4px solid #daa520;
        }
        .considerations-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #b8860b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .considerations-list {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: #b8860b;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="document-container">
        <!-- Recording Information Block -->
        <div class="recording-info">
            <div class="recording-grid">
                <div class="recording-row">
                    <div class="recording-cell recording-label">Requested by:</div>
                    <div class="recording-cell">{{ requested_by }}</div>
                </div>
                {% if apn %}
                <div class="recording-row">
                    <div class="recording-cell recording-label">APN:</div>
                    <div class="recording-cell">{{ apn }}</div>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="recording-row">
                    <div class="recording-cell recording-label">Mail to:</div>
                    <div class="recording-cell">
                        {% if return_to.name %}{{ return_to.name }}<br>{% endif %}
                        {% if return_to.address %}{{ return_to.address | replace('\n', '<br>') | safe }}{% endif %}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Document Title -->
        <div class="header-section">
            <div class="document-title">Interspousal Transfer Deed</div>
            <div>{{ county }} County, California</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Interspousal Transfer Notice -->
        <div class="interspousal-notice">
            <div class="interspousal-notice-title">üíç Interspousal Transfer üíç</div>
            <div class="interspousal-notice-text">
                TRANSFER BETWEEN MARRIED SPOUSES<br>
                PURSUANT TO CALIFORNIA FAMILY CODE
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tax Exemption Section -->
        {% if tax_exempt %}
        <div class="tax-exemption">
            <strong>Documentary Transfer Tax:</strong> EXEMPT<br>
            <strong>Reason:</strong> {{ exemption_reason }}<br>
            <strong>Legal Basis:</strong> Revenue & Taxation Code ¬ß11927 - Interspousal transfers are exempt from documentary transfer tax
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <!-- Parties Section -->
        <div class="parties-section">
            <div class="parties-title">Parties to this Transfer</div>
            
            <p><strong>TRANSFEROR SPOUSE:</strong></p>
            <p>{{ grantors_text }}</p>
            
            <p><strong>TRANSFEREE SPOUSE:</strong></p>
            <p>{{ grantees_text }}</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Transfer Clause -->
        <div class="transfer-clause">
            <p>The above-named Transferor Spouse hereby GRANTS, TRANSFERS, and CONVEYS to the above-named Transferee Spouse, 
            as his/her separate property, all right, title, and interest in and to the following described real property 
            situated in {{ county }} County, California:</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Legal Description -->
        <div class="legal-description">
            <div class="legal-description-title">Legal Description</div>
            <p>{{ legal_description }}</p>
            
            {% if apn %}
            <p><strong>Assessor's Parcel Number:</strong> {{ apn }}</p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <!-- Property Characterization -->
        <div class="property-characterization">
            <div class="characterization-title">Property Characterization</div>
            <p><strong>The above-described property is hereby characterized as:</strong></p>
            <p style="font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; color: #228b22;">
                {{ property_characterization | upper }}
            </p>
            <p><em>This characterization is made pursuant to California Family Code ¬ß¬ß 1100 et seq. and affects the legal 
            ownership and rights of the spouses with respect to this property.</em></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Legal Considerations -->
        <div class="legal-considerations">
            <div class="considerations-title">Important Legal Considerations</div>
            <ul class="considerations-list">
                <li><strong>Tax Implications:</strong> This transfer may have income tax, gift tax, or property tax consequences. Consult a tax professional.</li>
                <li><strong>Creditor Protection:</strong> Changing property characterization may affect protection from creditors of either spouse.</li>
                <li><strong>Estate Planning:</strong> This transfer may affect estate planning strategies and should be coordinated with existing wills or trusts.</li>
                <li><strong>Divorce Considerations:</strong> In the event of divorce, separate property is generally not subject to equal division.</li>
                <li><strong>Mortgage Implications:</strong> If the property is encumbered by a mortgage, lender consent may be required.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Execution Section -->
        <div class="execution-section">
            <p><strong>TO HAVE AND TO HOLD</strong> the above described property unto the said Transferee Spouse, 
            as his/her separate property, and to the heirs and assigns of said Transferee Spouse forever.</p>
            
            <p><strong>This transfer is made without consideration</strong> and is intended to change the character of the property 
            from community property (or the separate property of Transferor) to the separate property of Transferee Spouse.</p>
            
            <p><strong>Dated:</strong> {{ execution_date }}</p>
            
            <div class="signature-block">
                <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-label">Transferor Spouse</div>
                </div>
                
                <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-label">Transferee Spouse (Acknowledgment of Receipt)</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Notary Section -->
        <div class="notary-section">
            <div class="notary-title">Notary Acknowledgment</div>
            
            <div class="notary-text">
                <p>State of California</p>
                <p>County of {{ county }}</p>
                
                <p>On ________________, before me, ________________________________,
                personally appeared ________________________________,
                who proved to me on the basis of satisfactory evidence to be the person(s) whose name(s) is/are 
                subscribed to the within instrument and acknowledged to me that he/she/they executed the same in 
                his/her/their authorized capacity, and that by his/her/their signature(s) on the instrument the 
                person(s), or the entity upon behalf of which the person(s) acted, executed the instrument.</p>
                
                <p>I certify under PENALTY OF PERJURY under the laws of the State of California that the foregoing 
                paragraph is true and correct.</p>
                
                <p>WITNESS my hand and official seal.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="notary-signature-block">
                <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-label">Signature of Notary Public</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Spousal Consent Notice -->
        <div class="interspousal-notice" style="margin-top: 40px;">
            <div class="interspousal-notice-title">Spousal Consent Confirmation</div>
            <div class="interspousal-notice-text">
                BOTH SPOUSES HAVE CONSENTED TO THIS TRANSFER<br>
                AS EVIDENCED BY THEIR SIGNATURES ABOVE<br>
                PURSUANT TO FAMILY CODE ¬ß 1100
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Document Metadata -->
        <div style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 8pt; color: #999; text-align: center;">
            Generated: {{ generated_at }} | Document Type: {{ document_type }} | Version: {{ generator_version }}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


